social_posts.post_text: Christmas parties! Marry someone who can do both, right?😁🎄
Another great Christmas in the books! Hope y’all enjoyed your holidays🎅🏻🎄 See you tomorrow at Bridgestone😁

A little late I know, but how do you summarize the best year of your life? 🤷🏻‍♂️ Here’s what I came up with, and here’s to trying to beat 2022 with an even better 2023! 😁And maybe I can even learn how to make videos not blurry😂 Happy new year y’all! 🎆🎉
The feeling when you win 3 straight right before the break 😁 see y’all back in the Bridgey soon! ☀️🔋
Bye week and my best friend’s birthday at the same time is something we adore! So lucky to call you my wife @erinalvey, I love you so much! Happy birthday baby!🎂🎉❤️

Repping a new Gold and Blue 🏒 

Welcome N, @forsbergfilip | #EveryoneN

Extremely excited to join the ownership group for @nashvillesc ⚽️ Soccer has always played a huge part in my life, and this takes that to the next level! Can’t wait to be a part of this club and the city’s continued growth, Let’s go NSC!! 💛💙 #EveryoneN

First picture summarizes my season pretty well. Toughest part of my career so far, watching from the sidelines while the boys battled through all kinds of adversity, but couldn’t be more proud of them! Can’t wait to be back out there with the boys again, in front of the best fans in the league! Thankful for all the support I’ve received, See y’all soon 🟡🔵
When you think your scooter’s battery is low, but you find out it’s fully charged and ready to roll 😐➡️😄🛵 #scooterlife
Off season. Lots of uncaptured fun work in the gym, lots of captured fun outside it. Perfectly balanced, as all things should be🏋️😎
Midsommar in Leksand with friends and family is something I’ll never take for granted! 🌺☀️🌊
Grinding back where it all begun 🇸🇪 #Leksand
Happy anniversary my love! One year married, forever to go❤️ Can’t wait for all the fun we got ahead of us, we’re just getting started!! I love you so much @erinalvey
Birthday weekend in London😄⚽️🪄

The Hockey Clinic is one of the highlights of the year, and this one was the best one so far! Massive thank you to all the kids coming out and making it so special, and to all the coaches and staff at @fordicecenter and @predsfoundation for making this Clinic the best, year after year! 😄
@nhl Media tour ✅  Next up: Training Camp 🤠
Home opener was awesome as always, big win for the fellas! 🤠 Now off to Boston!
Wild one last night, @bridgestonearenaofficial was rocking!! 🔥 Back at it again tomorrow!🟡🔵
Life has provided lots of smiles, hugs and happiness lately, we will work hard to keep it that way! 😄
Baby Boy Forsberg joining the fun in May 2024👶🏼💙
